            <li><a href="/cases/" class="hover:text-red transition-colors">사례</a></li>
            <li><a href="/process/" class="hover:text-red transition-colors">운영 프로세스</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about/" class="hover:text-red transition-colors">회사 소개</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-bold text-white/90 mb-3">💬 문의</div>
